window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The carnival rolled into town, bringing an obsession so powerful that it threatened to unravel my entire existence.</p> <p>Seeking an escape from my monotonous life in Willow Creek, I eagerly stepped into the carnival's vibrant chaos, unaware that everything was about to change. I was simply chasing a thrill, never expecting to stumble into the arms of Larsâ€”a captivating mechanic shrouded in mystery.</p> <p>But a dark underworld of secrets and shadows lurks beneath the carnival's dazzling facade. The deeper I fall into Lars's enigmatic world, the more I realize that love can be as intoxicating as it is dangerous. Lars teeters on the edge between passion and obsession, and our connection threatens to overwhelm us.</p> <p>With each reckless adventure, I'm torn between the exhilarating allure of his world and the terrifying fear of losing my own. As our relationship intensifies, I'm forced to confront a haunting question: can love survive amidst the chaos, or will I be lost forever in his darkness?</p> <p>Step right up, if you dare, because this thrilling ride is about to begin.</p> <p>Carnival Obsession is a dark romance novella with heavy subjects that some listeners may find triggering. There's a full list of the trigger warnings on my website. This story has no cliffhanger and ends with a HEA.</p>"; 
